3d738bd5cfbf9119105f213f1","tid":1868070,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:36:42.000Z","msg":"刻意將離境地點由「中國」改為「香港」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}